{"tid":2479084,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅冠聰獲英國批出政治庇護","createTime":"2021-04-07T14:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T14:23:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"14b28efba847dc7a14eafe51f6d3d093085aecd5","tid":2479084,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1379798987415248898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1379798987415248898&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=8221ae8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1379798987415248898&h=4c986e17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1379798987415248898</a>"},{"pid":"21014cbe7cd7b5d83ae8707c33f2868758ba0cdc","tid":2479084,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZcBcbTHDfLCavAMpc9fPwDCecx4DAtU42Gqw2gUa2Kzu?filename=nukDuFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnukDuFR.jpg&h=2099c367&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0e5c9ea46e26de66e8434dfad35da5f57e10c96","tid":2479084,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a26fa04bfbeb71adf1aed4dce0f87525b2c594","tid":2479084,"uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:14:21.000Z","msg":"「根據1951日內瓦公約下對於難民地位的定義，你已被視為難民以及按照移民法下獲批庇護。你獲得於規定時間內逗留英國的許可。」<br />\n<br />\n經歷約四個月的申請，多輪與難民審批機關的會面、會談，我早前已接獲英國內政部的通知，庇護申請經已獲批。在我的個案中，基於我面對過的政治案件、中共在國安法下的通緝，諸多證據顯示我是因政治迫害而被迫離開家園，且在可見將來無法回國。<br />\n<br />\n然而，我的審批狀況並不代表大多手足所面對的處境。他們的個案不一定獲媒體關注從而有新聞佐證，也可能會因案件內容涉及武力衝突而被質疑，或者是因戰友被捕而產生恐懼並離開香港卻沒有具體證據。這些朋友在面對難民審批時未必能立即給予充足證據，在等待面試和結果時伴隨對未來的迷茫和焦慮。因此，很多流亡抗爭者所面對的困難並非一句「申請難民」就可以解決。<br />\n<br />\n我希望我的個案能夠使英國內政部相關部門更了解香港複雜的政治局勢，並儘量給予手足們一定的酌情權，在不損害難民申請的門檻準則時，確保受逼害的抗爭者能夠逗留在安全的地方。<br />\n<br />\n感謝所有在過程中給予我意見以及搜集資料的朋友，也希望離散在世界各地的手足一切順利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2519151041569547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F2519151041569547&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYdB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=815a2db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2519151041569547</a>"},{"pid":"e921a24679b61c9896c5080b099ae0c56f949b1b","tid":2479084,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28024c5ec41855c8a5a2f6f00d4f869a06bde52a","tid":2479084,"uid":82938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:14:49.000Z","msg":"唔批就奇啦佢既名氣<br />\n又係前垃會"},{"pid":"07423aa38fe137392ad5f4a005c7bd83bc59e350","tid":2479084,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"9395e8242b4797238e06d5b21234e3692ceffd55","tid":2479084,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:15:53.000Z","msg":"佢打國際線好有力 <br />\n好人一生平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f8e189700c62ae0dca51f0a2e4725615a2cc01","tid":2479084,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21014cbe7cd7b5d83ae8707c33f2868758ba0cdc","tid":2479084,"uid":362346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T14:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nukDuFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http